egories": [{"id": 2, "description": "單人"}, {"id": 22, "description": "Steam 成就"}, {"id": 23, "description": "Steam 雲端"}, {"id": 62, "description": "親友同享"}], "genres": [{"id": "4", "description": "休閒"}, {"id": "23", "description": "獨立製作"}, {"id": "3", "description": "角色扮演"}, {"id": "28", "description": "模擬"}], "release_date": {"coming_soon": false, "date": "2025 年 9 月 22 日"}}}}, "us": {"3063290": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "My Classmate is AV Actress", "steam_appid": 3063290, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063290/extras/c546a132aa627ff0d3b36e6863ebc63e.poster.avif?t=1773956450\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063290/extras/c546a132aa627ff0d3b36e6863ebc63e.webm?t=1773956450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063290/extras/c546a132aa627ff0d3b36e6863ebc63e.mp4?t=1773956450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063290/extras/7a54323ec2cc2dca8d78bb9c99d5a88e.avif?t=1773956450\" width=435 height=69 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>After being dumped by my girlfriend due to poor sexual skills, a familiar-looking Japanese girl transfers into my department. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>To my surprise, she turns out to be an active AV actress! Not only is she willing to teach me how to improve my skills, but she also encourages me to hook up with others to gain experience. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>With things coming this far, there’s no turning back—I’m determined to master techniques that even an AV actress can't handle.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063290/extras/a0144c30601f09f7682350f4117e4065.avif?t=1773956450\" width=435 height=69 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>※Visual Novel Gameplay</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>As the story progresses, players will encounter multiple characters and engage in deep interactions, advancing the plot. The gameplay is linear, with no choices, allowing players to focus on experiencing the narrative.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>※Intimate dynamic CGs</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>There are multiple CGs for all five characters in the game, and through dynamic performances throughout the entire process, every intense moment of physical interweaving with the female characters is more clearly shown.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>※Growing up</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Your will encounter various female characters over the course of a little more than a month.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Each day is divided into three time periods: <u>Morning</u>, <u>Afternoon</u>, and </strong><u>Evening</u><strong>.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>During each period, players can choose one action from <u>Work</u>, <u>Training</u>, or <u>Hookup</u>, which is only available at night.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>By planning different activities to improve your abilities, you can increase the female characters’ affection and gradually deepen your relationships with them through the main storyline and various events!</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>※Learning from Hookups</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> <u>Hookup </u>can only be conducted at night. You can take the other person to different dates to increase your favorability, and finally push them into bed to accumulate practical experience.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>※Turning Money into Progress</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the shop, you can exchange the money you've earned for various items that help you improve faster or increase the affection of female characters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some items are essential for reaching a happy ending!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063290/extras/b0dbeb37a3d7ace973348136d5624051.avif?t=1773956450\" width=435 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063290/extras/87deec4fa59d9b2629684c8140946979.avif?t=1773956450\" width=610 height=620 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063290/extras/4a3dbeb08100fc962960ae47c2d3dabc.avif?t=1773956450\" width=610 height=620 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063290/extras/451ea0bc8421a5415f2d8df6aedfd8f3.avif?t=1773956450\" width=610 height=620 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063290/extras/04d5c2ca363f04b5a078b43bbd97ded0.avif?t=1773956450\" width=610 height=620 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063290/extras/b76bba7bcff7e081c3c902fbc992ce96.avif?t=1773956450\" width=610 height=620 /></span></p>", "about_the_game": "<p clas